From: Ren Wang <iamwrm@gmail.com>
Date: Sun, 19 Jul 2026 11:15:49 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 08/11] Add Anthropic Claude-plan OAuth flow, storage, and CLI

Port pi's Anthropic (Claude Pro/Max) PKCE browser authentication flow with
a paste-the-code fallback (claude.ai's code#state format). Store the
isolated refreshable credential in ~/.grok/anthropic_auth.json and expose
grok anthropic login, logout, and status commands.
